@page "/About"

<div class="container-fluid bg-light py-md-5 py-3 shadow-sm">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/016/765/134/non_2x/about-us-button-web-banner-templates-illustration-vector.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Summer sale banner">
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Want to know more?</h1>
                <p class="lead">Get some insight into what we are about!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid bg-white shadow-sm py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="lead px-md-5 px-3">
            We do things and it's cool stuff. Our products are always good. We get them from good places, and we don't do bad stuff because we hate bad stuff! <br/>
            Always keep in mind that we are a morally good company, and you can trust that we always provide good quality, good service, and nothing morally dubious ever. <br/>
            In fact, we take this so seriously that you don't ever have to look into our company's history. Please don't. <br/>
            Thank you!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="container-fluid bg-light shadow-sm py-md-5 py-3 text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-around gap-3">
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="bg-white py-5 rounded shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-ban fs-1 text-danger"></i>
                    <h5 class="mt-2">No bad stuff</h5>
                    <p class="p-3">All of us here hate bad stuff and we don't sell any of it. <br/>
                        If you find any bad stuff no you didn't.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="bg-white py-5 rounded shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-bug fs-1 text-success"></i>
                    <h5 class="mt-2">Bug reports</h5>
                    <p class="p-3">If you find any issues with our site, please let us know! <br/>
                        Report any issues via our <a href="/Contact">contact page</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



